@baseUrl = http://localhost:8096

###
### URL Shortener API Tests
### Controller: ShortenerApiController
### Validation: @NotBlank, @ValidUrl, @Size(max = 2048) on url parameter (400 Bad Request on violation)
### Response: Returns plain text shortened URL on success
### Error format: application/json structured ErrorResponse object for validation and other API errors
###

### Shorten URL - Valid HTTPS URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=https://example.com
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Valid HTTP URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=http://example.com
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Complex URL with parameters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=https://example.com/path?param1=value1&param2=value2#section
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Long URL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?
    url=https://example.com/very/long/path/with/many/segments/and/parameters?param1=value1&param2=value2&param3=value3&
    param4=value4
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Invalid URL (missing protocol)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=example.com
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Invalid URL (malformed)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=not-a-url
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Empty URL (expects 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - Missing URL parameter (expects 400 Bad Request)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - URL with special characters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=https://example.com/path with spaces
Accept: text/plain

### Shorten URL - URL with encoded characters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/url-shortener/shorten?url=https://example.com/%7Euser%2Fprofile%3Fid%3D123
Accept: text/plain

